{"tid":2031290,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港係一個淪常悲劇既受害者","createTime":"2020-05-23T09:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:50:20.000Z","uid":37038,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"81d9518298f76436aa8025a828272ca7297f8c1a","tid":2031290,"uid":37038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:58:35.000Z","msg":"從前有個小朋友叫香港,<br />\n係一個混血兒,<br />\n親生老豆係中國人叫大陸,<br />\n親生阿媽係外國人叫英國.<br />\n<br />\n老豆好有錢同有好多兒女,<br />\n有上海仔, 深圳仔, 大灣仔 ...<br />\n香港仔個阿媽係老豆個二奶,<br />\n無名無份.<br />\n<br />\n有一日,<br />\n老豆做左好多衰野,<br />\n阿媽開始頂唔住要分手,<br />\n老豆份人個腦最重視係錢,<br />\n佢宜家好擔心個阿媽借香港仔有血緣身份搶佢身家同爆佢大鍋,<br />\n為左唔俾阿媽報警同分身家,<br />\n決定親手殺左自己親生仔,<br />\n同阿媽劃清界線.<br />\n<br />\n即使佢知道果個係佢親生仔,<br />\n佢最尾都親手殺左.<br />\n<br />\n因為佢眼中最緊要係錢,<br />\n而且佢唔係得一個仔.<br />\n仲要老豆以前都殺過人,<br />\n對殺人冇任何恐懼."},{"pid":"9ff5ea26afe591dfd84e59957ce9d46b51e23a5b","tid":2031290,"uid":340631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:01:47.000Z","msg":"好撚有感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012d2103bdd5e66d89a44b9f62da609c292a968a","tid":2031290,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:01:55.000Z","msg":"結論是？"},{"pid":"3f926e991f99e976a3584f3fd3670a53a703f1d6","tid":2031290,"uid":75394,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:03:42.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n香港就係香港<br />\n乜撚嘢親生老豆係中國人叫大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你自己認賊作父"},{"pid":"4db5d5b99c58eff0deeb1c2e6357ab6a88583207","tid":2031290,"uid":37038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f926e991f99e976a3584f3fd3670a53a703f1d6","tid":2031290,"uid":75394,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedB